http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/ss/wampanoag_tribe.htm 205.168.79.33 19970115074128 text/html 8660
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 07:41:29 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Mon, 09 Dec 1996 21:55:29 GMT
