<html><head><title>CESD: Slide Shows: Rural</title></head><body BGCOLOR = #FFFFFF><A HREF="/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/ncsdicon.gif" ALT="= NCSD Home Page ="></A><A HREF="/slideshows/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/bugs/slides.gif" alt="= Slide Shows =""></a><p><b><a href="/slides/rural/index.html">Act Locally Slide Show</a></b><br><i>National Center for Appropriate Technology</i><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p><center><a href="l/38.gif"><img src="t/38.gif"></a></center><p><!--**head**--> RuralAction's environmental staff provides guidance and assistance to the RestoreCorps Program, which "mobilizes local people to undertake community and ecological restoration projects in their own communities."	RestoreCorps relies upon collaboration. Participating organizations and individuals include: a VISTA volunteer; the Ohio Department of Natural Resources Forestry Division; the Wayne National Forest; the Athens County Arbor Day Committee; the Hocking Valley Greens; The Phar Cycle (a local support center for area youth); Athens County Juvenile Courts; and, AppalAction, the student division of RuralAction.<!--**foot**--><p><a href = "37.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/prev_button.gif" alt = "=Previous="></a><a href = "/slides/rural/index.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/toc_button.gif" alt = "=Table of Content="></a><a href = "39.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/next_button.gif" alt = "=Next="></a><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><address><p><a href="/rsc/comment-form.shtml">Comments &amp; Questions</a></i><b> | </b><i><a href="/rsc/suggest.shtml">Suggest a Resource</a></i></address><h5>URL: http://<a href="http://solstice.crest.org/">solstice.crest.org</a>/<a href="/">doe</a>/<a href="/">sustainable</a>/<a href="/slideshows/">slideshows</a>/<a href="/slides/rural">rural</a>/38.html</h5></body></html>
