<html><head><title>CESD: Slide Shows: Rural</title></head><body BGCOLOR = #FFFFFF><A HREF="/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/ncsdicon.gif" ALT="= NCSD Home Page ="></A><A HREF="/slideshows/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/bugs/slides.gif" alt="= Slide Shows =""></a><p><b><a href="/slides/rural/index.html">Act Locally Slide Show</a></b><br><i>National Center for Appropriate Technology</i><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p><center><a href="l/73.gif"><img src="t/73.gif"></a></center><p><!--**head**--> In five years, the Jefferson Parish Christmas Tree/Marsh Restoration Program has recycled more than 350,000 Christmas trees; constructed 18,000 linear feet of shoreline fences, and filled five abandoned, dead-end canals. Program participants estimate that the work to date will, over time, restore more than 40 acres of wetlands and protect additional acreage.<!--**foot**--><p><a href = "72.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/prev_button.gif" alt = "=Previous="></a><a href = "/slides/rural/index.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/toc_button.gif" alt = "=Table of Content="></a><a href = "74.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/next_button.gif" alt = "=Next="></a><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><address><p><a href="/rsc/comment-form.shtml">Comments &amp; Questions</a></i><b> | </b><i><a href="/rsc/suggest.shtml">Suggest a Resource</a></i></address><h5>URL: http://<a href="http://solstice.crest.org/">solstice.crest.org</a>/<a href="/">doe</a>/<a href="/">sustainable</a>/<a href="/slideshows/">slideshows</a>/<a href="/slides/rural">rural</a>/73.html</h5></body></html>
