<html><head><title>CESD: Slide Shows: Rural</title></head><body BGCOLOR = #FFFFFF><A HREF="/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/ncsdicon.gif" ALT="= NCSD Home Page ="></A><A HREF="/slideshows/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/bugs/slides.gif" alt="= Slide Shows =""></a><p><b><a href="/slides/rural/index.html">Act Locally Slide Show</a></b><br><i>National Center for Appropriate Technology</i><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p><center><a href="l/40.gif"><img src="t/40.gif"></a></center><p><!--**head**--> RuralAction's diverse efforts in the region include assisting and organizing local recycling efforts like the one pictured here, where volunteers load trucks with old appliances during an "Ultimate Recycling Day" in Athens, Ohio.<!--**foot**--><p><a href = "39.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/prev_button.gif" alt = "=Previous="></a><a href = "/slides/rural/index.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/toc_button.gif" alt = "=Table of Content="></a><a href = "41.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/next_button.gif" alt = "=Next="></a><p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><address><p><a href="/rsc/comment-form.shtml">Comments &amp; Questions</a></i><b> | </b><i><a href="/rsc/suggest.shtml">Suggest a Resource</a></i></address><h5>URL: http://<a href="http://solstice.crest.org/">solstice.crest.org</a>/<a href="/">doe</a>/<a href="/">sustainable</a>/<a href="/slideshows/">slideshows</a>/<a href="/slides/rural">rural</a>/40.html</h5></body></html>
