<!--**head**-->



Some Accepted Definitions:<p>
	<I>"Sustainability is about fairness over time; it means applying the Golden Rule to future generations."</I><br>
	- from "Description of a Toolkit for Sustainably Redeveloping Communities," prepared for DOE by Helen J. Kessler, Sieben Associates.
<p>	
 There are a number of accepted definitions for sustainable development.


