<p>

<!--**head**-->



 Denver is one of 36 communities that have enrolled in the U.S. Department of Energy's "Clean Cities" program. As such, city officials have made a commitment to use clean, alternative transportation fuels and to employ other methods to reduce the production of air pollutants.


<!--**foot**--><p>
