<DOCNO>WT26-B27-206</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000337-B031-236</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/slideshows/urban/17.html 205.168.79.33 19970115083710 text/html 2441
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 08:37:08 GMT
