<!--**head**-->



 Old toilets were returned, crushed and mixed with gravel to be used as a base for road-paving material. The bags in this slide are filled with crushed toilet pieces ready for use. Much of this road-base has been used to repair street and freeway damage caused by the last big Los Angeles-area earthquake.








