<p>

<!--**head**-->


			
 In places like Chattanooga, Portland, East Los Angeles, Newark, and Denver, residents and sustainability experts have teamed up to build a new future.
	And, during a time of mushrooming population growth coupled with diminishing resources, a new future is what we all need. 

For us. For our children.


