<DOCNO>WT26-B27-278</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000340-B036-431</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/slideshows/urban/67.html 205.168.79.33 19970115102013 text/html 2113
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 10:20:10 GMT
