<html><head><title>CESD: Slide Shows: Urban</title></head><body BGCOLOR = #FFFFFF>

<A HREF="/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/ncsdicon.gif" ALT="= CESD Home Page ="></A>
<A HREF="/slideshows/"><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="/rsc/bugs/slides.gif" alt = "= Slide Shows ="></a>
<p>

<b><a href="/slideshows/urban/index.html">Sustainable Development Slideshow</a></b><br>
<i>National Center for Appropriate Technology</i>


<p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p>
<center><a href="l/13.gif"><img src="t/13.gif"></a></center>
<p>

<!--**head**-->


	<I>"Sustainable development is development that meets the needs of the present without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own needs."</I><br>
	- from the United Nations World Commission on Environment and Development
<p>
 In 1987, the United Nations World Commission on Environment and Development published a report on the health of the global community. The report highlighted the inter-dependence between the environment and economic development. It coined the definition quoted here, which is repeated widely in books and pamphlets on the subject of "sustainability." 


<!--**foot**--><p>
<a href = "12.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/prev_button.gif" alt = "=Previous="></a>
<a href = "/slideshows/urban/index.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/toc_button.gif" alt = "=Table of Content="></a>
<a href = "14.html"><img src="http://solstice.crest.org/common/next_button.gif" alt = "=Next="></a>
<p><img SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p>
