<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Sunsphere City</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000"><P ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="index.shtml"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_home.gif"ALT="Front Page" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="zine.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_zine.gif"ALT="The 'Zine" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="market.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_market.gif"ALT=" Marketplace" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="bonus.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_bonus.gif"ALT="Bonus Track" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<P ALIGN=Center><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/pagehead.gif" ALT="Metro Pulse Online" WIDTH="389" HEIGHT="8"><BR>
<IMG SRC="dir_suncity/head_suncity.gif" ALT="Sunsphere City"WIDTH="411" HEIGHT="36"><BR>
<A HREF="search.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_search.gif" ALT="Search" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="3"></A>
<BR><IMG ALIGN=Left SRC="dir_suncity/skyline.gif" WIDTH="261" HEIGHT="134"HSPACE="10">
<H3>If you weren't here during the '82 World's Fair...</H3>
<P>...then you probably don't recall the New York Times referring to
Knoxville as a "scruffy little city." Well, 'round these parts, we take pride in our scruff. Listed below is a compendium of enough of it to keep you busy for a while, even if this ain't New York.
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<TABLE WIDTH="340" CELLSPACING="20"><TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><P ALIGN=Left><A HREF="dir_suncity/calendar_dir/calendar.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_calendar.gif" ALT="Event Calendar" WIDTH="85"HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR>Hey, it's the best events calendar in Knoxville.
Really.
<HR><A HREF="dir_suncity/venues_dir/venues.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_venues.gif"ALT="Clubs & Venues" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR>
Where to go to see the show. Tickets, too.
<HR><A HREF="dir_suncity/band_dir/menu_local.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_band_local.gif"ALT="LocalBands" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR>An archive of Metro Pulse
articles on local
bands.</TD>
<TD><A HREF="dir_suncity/movies_dir/menu.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_cinemetro.gif" ALT="Cinemetropolis" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR>Metro Pulse Movie Blurbs, theater schedules, the Movie Guru, and more, all coming to a screen near you. Right in front of you, in fact.
<HR><A HREF="dir_suncity/bok_dir/bok96.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_bok.gif"ALT="Best of Knoxville"WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR>What's on top in Kville? Take a
gander at the results of our Third Annual Readers' Poll.</TD>
<TD><A HREF="dir_suncity/rg_dir/rg96s.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="graphics_misc/b_rg.gif"ALT="Restaurant Guide"WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="2"></A><BR><A HREF="dir_suncity/rg_dir/rg96s.html">Complete
