<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="dir_bonus/bonus.gif" WIDTH="198" HEIGHT="198" HSPACE="10" ALT="wacky 'ol graphic">
<IMG SRC="dir_bonus/joe_ian.gif" HEIGHT=133 WIDTH=133 HSPACE=5 ALIGN=LEFT>What <STRONG>is</STRONG> the secret connection between publisher Joe Sullivan and systems manager Ian Blackburn?
<H2>Welcome to the Bonus Track</H2>This is the place we stick the stuff that we can't (or simply don't) run in the paper, stuff that doesn't fit in any other category, and anything we arbitrarily decide is amusing. There'll be more to come as soon as our webmonkey finds the time to cobble it together.
<P>Got a neat suggestion? Don't keep it to yourself - <A HREF="MAILTO: jojo@metropulse.com">write to our webmonkey!</A><BR CLEAR=ALL>

<P><TABLE BORDER CELLPADDING="5">

<TR VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><IMG SRC="dir_bonus/survey_dir/survey_icon.gif" WIDTH="50" HEIGHT="47" ALT="Reader Survey"></TD>
<TD><A HREF="dir_bonus/survey_dir/survey.shtml"><STRONG>Reader Survey:</STRONG></A> What exactly <STRONG>do</STRONG> you think, anyway?</TD></TR>

<TR VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><IMG SRC="dir_bonus/metroblab_icon.gif" WIDTH="48" HEIGHT="47" ALT="MetroBlab"></TD>
<TD><A HREF="metroblab/metroblab.html"><STRONG>MetroBlab:</STRONG></A> A message board. Rant & rave. Blithely comment on the sociopolitical concerns of our fair city. Spew invective. Rock on.</TD></TR>

<TR VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><IMG SRC="dir_bonus/egos_dir/egos_icon.gif" WIDTH="50" HEIGHT="47" ALT="Egos-A-Go-Go"></TD>
<TD><A HREF="dir_bonus/egos_dir/egos.html"><STRONG>Egos-A-Go-Go:</STRONG></A> Personal web pages handcrafted by our stalwart citizens.</TD>

<TR VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><IMG SRC="dir_bonus/aan_dir/aan_icon.gif" WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="47" ALT="AAN"></TD>
<TD><A HREF="dir_bonus/aan_dir/aan.html"><STRONG>Directory of AAN papers:</STRONG></A> There's only one Metro Pulse, but there's something like it in most cities of our size or bigger. Herein is a directory of Association of Alternative Newsweeklies papers across North America.</TD></TR>

</TABLE>

