<P ALIGN=Center>
<IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="head_calendar.gif" ALT="The Metro Pulse Entertainment
Calendar" WIDTH="411" HEIGHT="36">
<A HREF="spotlights.html"><IMG SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_spotlights.gif" ALT="Spotlights" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="3"></A>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="guidelines.html">Calendar Submission Guidelines</A>
