<P><STRONG>HOLIDAY FESTIVAL OF ONE ACT COMEDIES</STRONG> ACTORS STUDIO 5213 Homberg Dr. Thru Jan. 11. Shows are Thurs.-Sat. 8pm. Tickets are $10 Thurs., $12 Fri. and Sat. (588-6113)
<P><STRONG>STAGE DOOR</STRONG> ACTORS STUDIO 5213 Homberg Dr. Join the open mike theater showcase and improv showdown. Sign up and perform original works of song, poetry, and monologues. Jan. 15. Show is 8pm. Admission is $6/$5 students. (588-6113)
<P><STRONG>I STAND BEFORE YOU NAKED</STRONG> TOMATO HEAD Market Square. Jan. 16-25. Shows are Thurs. 9pm, Fri. and Sat. 10pm. Tickets are $5. (637-4067)
<P><STRONG>WILL YOU STILL LOVE ME IN THE MORNING?</STRONG> WEST SIDE DINNER THEATRE 12801 Kingston Pk. Thru Feb. 1. Shows are Thurs..-Sat. 8:15pm, with a buffet at 6:45pm. Tickets are $18 for play and buffet. Reservations are required and must be made by 2pm on day of attendance. (966-8768)
<P><STRONG>CRIMES OF THE HEART</STRONG> HARLEQUIN DINNER THEATRE 7213 Kingston Pk. Sit down to dinner with a performance of Beth Henley's Pulitzer Prize-winning play. Thru Feb. 16. Shows are Fri. and Sat. 8pm; dinner at 6:45pm. Tickets are $15, or $24-$30 for play and dinner. Reservations are required and must be made one day in advance. (558-0181)

