<P><STRONG>THE BIJOU THEATRICAL ACADEMY</STRONG> offers drama classes in January. Little People's Theatre (ages 5-8), Theatre for Young People (ages 9-12), and Teen Workshop (ages 13-17) meet on Saturdays beginning Jan. 18 and continue through Feb. 25. Cost is $80. Also, a mini-session in costuming, for ages 7 and up, will be held through Feb. 8. To register, call 525-2295.
