<P><STRONG>Kaya Korean
<BR></STRONG>149 Montvue Rd., 691-0237
<BR>    One of the most unique Asian restaurants in town, Kaya serves authentic
Korean cuisine. That means hae mool pa jun (seafood pancake), bulkoki (barbecue),
bibim bab (marinated sea and land vegetables), and jap chae (marinated noodles).
The weekend lunch buffet is among the best in town, 12pm-3pm. Karaoke after
9pm. Lunch: Tues.-Fri. 11am-3pm, Dinner: Sun.-Sat. 5pm-10pm $7-$12. V/MC.
Beer and wine.
