<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Metro Pulse Restaurant Guide</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000"><P ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="../../index.shtml"><IMG ALIGN=Middle  SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_home.gif" ALT="Front Page" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../zine.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle  SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_zine.gif" ALT="The 'Zine" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../suncity.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle  SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_suncity.gif" ALT="Sunsphere City" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../market.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle  SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_market.gif" ALT=" Marketplace" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../bonus.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle  SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_bonus.gif" ALT="Bonus Track" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="head_rg.gif" WIDTH="411" HEIGHT="36" ALT="Restaurant Guide"><BR><A HREF="rg96s.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_full.gif" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" VSPACE="3"></A>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="hed_east.gif" ALT="East Knoxville" WIDTH="242" HEIGHT="27">
<H2>BBQ
</H2><P><STRONG>Scruggs Real Pit Barbeque &amp; Package Store
<BR></STRONG>1920 Magnolia Ave., 524-4333
<BR>       What more do you need? Real deal 'que, and--if you get it to go--your
choice of beer, wine or liquor from their full-service package store. Mon.-Thurs.
10am-9pm, Fri.-Sat. 10am-midnight, open varying hours Sundays. Under $7-$12.
No credit cards. Beer, wine, liquor for off-premises consumption only.
<P><STRONG>Tic-Toc
<BR></STRONG>3240 E. Magnolia Ave., 522-6901
<BR>       An East Knoxville barbecue icon of the "dry" variety. Mon.-Sat.
10am-10pm.
Under $7. No credit cards. Beer only.
<H2>Cafe
</H2><P><STRONG>Tiger Tops Cafe
<BR></STRONG>Knoxville Zoo, 637-5331
<BR>        A cabin-like family lunch spot with a greenery and seasonal deck.
Soups
and sandwiches available and daily dessert specials. Perfect before or after
a visit to the Zoo, but admission is not required. Sun-Sat. 11am-3pm. Under
$7. V/MC/D/DC. No alcohol.
<H2>Coffee Shop
</H2><P><STRONG>Ruby's Coffee Shop
<BR></STRONG>3920 Martin Luther King Ave., 522-0782
<BR>    In the heart of East Knoxville, Ruby's serves family-style breakfast
('til
11am) and plate lunch specials. And they open in time for the most ambitious
fishermen to grab some biscuits and gravy on their way to the pond. Mon.-Fri.
5:30am-1:30pm, Sat. 5:30am-11am, closed Sundays. No credit cards. No alcohol.
<H2>Diner
</H2><P><STRONG>Heath's Cafe
<BR></STRONG>1916 Schofield Ave., 525-3877
<BR>    Hit this Lonsdale institution for a down-home meat-'n-three, and
some
of the best fried chicken in town. Mon.-Sat. 6am-8pm, Sun. 6am-2pm. Under
$7. No credit cards. No alcohol.
<H2>Philippine
</H2><P><STRONG>Philippine Connection
<BR></STRONG>3225 E. Magnolia Ave., 522-5276
<BR>    Wonderful Philippine food to take out. Try the lumpias or pancit
guisado.
Mon.-Sat. 11am-10pm. Under $7. No credit cards. No alcohol.
<H2>Pizza
</H2><P><STRONG>Pizza Palace
<BR></STRONG>3132 E. Magnolia Ave., 524-4388
<BR>    Drive-in pizza for that '50s experience: thin-crusted, simple pizza
with
loads and loads of cheese. An Eastside tradition. Under $12 Sun.-Thurs.
11am-11pm, Fri. &amp; Sat. 11am-1am. No credit cards. Beer only.
<P><HR>
</BODY></HTML>
