<TITLE>Metro Pulse Rate Card</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000"><P ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="../../index.shtml"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_home.gif" ALT="Front Page" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../zine.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_zine.gif" ALT="The 'Zine" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../suncity.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_suncity.gif" ALT="Sunsphere City" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../market.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_market.gif" ALT=" Marketplace" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<A HREF="../../bonus.html"><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="../../graphics_misc/b_bonus.gif" ALT="Bonus Track" WIDTH="85" HEIGHT="14" HSPACE="1"></A>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG ALIGN=Middle SRC="ratecard_head.gif" WIDTH="411" HEIGHT="36">
<P>
<IMG ALIGN=Left SRC="rate_stamp.gif" WIDTH="159" HEIGHT="170" HSPACE="10"><BR>
<H3>About Metro Pulse</H3>
<P>Metro Pulse is the weekly voice of Knoxville. This news, entertainment
and arts magazine is distributed free at more than 350 locations throughout
the metropolitan area with a total circulation of 28,500. An insightful,
timely and spirited editorial product makes Metro Pulse the local "medium
of choice" for sophisticated businesses and readers alike. Established in
1991, Metro Pulse is published by Metro Publications, Inc., a locally owned
and operated corporation.<BR CLEAR=ALL>

<H3>Readership Facts</H3>
<P><STRONG>Our reader... your customer</STRONG>
<BR>3.1 readers per copy<BR>Over 72,000 readers per week
<BR>Median age: 31 years old; 83% 18-44; 60% 25-49
<BR>Median income: $37,800; 35% earn $50,000+
<BR>70% are in professional/managerial/white collar positions
<BR>82% have some college or a college degree
<BR>30% have families with children under 18

<H3>Deadlines</H3>
<P><STRONG>Publication Day:</STRONG> Thursday<BR><STRONG>Space
Reservation:</STRONG> Wednesday, 4:30 pm, eight days prior to
publication<BR><STRONG>Copy Deadline:</STRONG> Thursday, 4:30 pm, seven days
prior to publication<BR><STRONG>Camera-Ready Ads:</STRONG> Monday, 4:30 pm,
four days prior to publication<BR><STRONG>Cancellations: </STRONG>Thursday,
11:00 am, seven days prior to publication
<P><EM>Ads cancelled after deadline
will be charged for space ordered and production services performed up to
that point</EM>.
<H3>Design/Production Services</H3>
<P>Metro Pulse and its award-winning ad design staff considers advertising
layout to be an integral part of its product image and customer service.
Basic ad design assistance, typesetting and layout are included in the display
advertising rates. Unusually time- and labor-intensive layout and design
requirements are handled at a rate of $40/hour, billed in 15 minute increments.
Contact your ad rep for details.
<H3>Production Department Fees and Policies</H3>
<P><STRONG>Standard photo shoot:</STRONG> $25/hr, $25
minimum<BR><STRONG>Custom photo shoot:</STRONG> quotes on
request<BR><STRONG>Photo prints:</STRONG>
$6/each<BR><STRONG>Halftones/scans:</STRONG> $6/each<BR><STRONG>Copy and
layout changes to ads:</STRONG> $10
<P><EM>Unless prior arrangements have been made, advertising design created
by Metro Pulse is the property of Metro Publications Inc. and&nbsp;may not
be used for other purposes without prior arrangement.</EM>
<P>Ads created
by Metro Pulse are available for use in other publications for a fee of $40.
Prints of ads for other promotional use (in-store promotion, direct mail,
etc.) are available for $10. Reworking of ads to fit custom size and layout
specifications are quoted on a case-by-case basis.
