<P><STRONG>Discounts</STRONG><BR>Payment on individual insertions within 10 days: 2%<BR>Pre-payment on individual insertions: 5%<BR>Pre-payment on entire contract run: 7%<BR>Consecutive ad run in contract (4x - 24x): 5%<BR>Camera-ready ad submission: 5%
<P><STRONG>Payment Policy</STRONG><BR>All advertising must be paid in advance unless a credit application is submitted and approved. Terms are net 30 days (10 days to qualify for 2% discount). Only those accounts in good standing are eligible for discounts listed above.<BR>We accept Visa/MasterCard.
<P><STRONG>Stipulations</STRONG><BR>Client is responsible for obtaining photo/logo/copy consent for all ad contend and will assume liability for all charges brought against Metro Publications, Inc. as a result of unauthorized content in advertisements.<BR>Metro Pulse will not be liable for damage of more than the cost of the space of the error in any advertisement.
