<P><STRONG>Policies:</STRONG> No refunds after submission. Canceled ads will receive credit for future advertising. Ads must be canceled before deadline for the issue in which the ad is scheduled to run. Ads are accepted upon the representation that the advertiser and/or its agency have the right to publish the contents thereof. In consideration of suck publication, advertiser and its agency agree to indemnify and hold the publisher harmless against any expense or loss by reason of any claims arising out of publication. The publisher reserves the right to edit, alter, omit, or refuse any advertising submitted.
